## Additional Terms for Albanian Bank Statement Converter

### Data Privacy and Security
This software is designed to process financial data locally without transmitting
sensitive information to external services. Users are responsible for ensuring
compliance with applicable data protection regulations including but not limited
to GDPR and Albanian data protection laws.

### Financial Data Handling
The software processes bank statements and financial data. Users must:
- Ensure proper security measures when deploying in production
- Implement appropriate access controls
- Follow local regulations for financial data processing
- Maintain audit logs as required by local authorities

### Bank-Specific Terms
This software is designed to work with Albanian banking formats and may not
be suitable for other banking systems without modification. The accuracy of
conversions depends on the consistency of bank statement formats.

### Limitation of Liability
The authors and contributors shall not be liable for any financial losses,
data corruption, or other damages arising from the use of this software.
Users should always verify converted data before importing into accounting
systems.

### Albanian Banking Compliance
This software is designed to comply with Albanian banking and accounting
standards as of 2025. Users are responsible for ensuring continued compliance
as regulations may change.

### QuickBooks Integration
This software generates CSV files compatible with QuickBooks. The authors
are not affiliated with Intuit Inc. or QuickBooks. Users should verify
compatibility with their specific QuickBooks version.